title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting table within a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data from tables within a grid cell, the data should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a grid. 
2. Attempt to export the data from the table within the grid cell. 
Follow these steps to export the data from tables within a grid cell without encountering any exceptions.
